ğŸ§  PROJECT OVERVIEW
Flow is a macOS app that visualizes cognitive load in real time â€” turning attention into something you can see, feel, and gently recover from.
Students often donâ€™t realize how fragmented their attention has become until productivity collapses. Flow makes this invisible mental state visible through a living, reactive orb that responds instantly to distraction, overload, and calm.
Flow is not a productivity tracker.
It is a mirror for attention.
The experience is intentionally calm, minimal, and premium â€” designed to feel unmistakably Apple-like. Every animation, sound, and interaction is purposeful. Nothing is noisy. Nothing is judgmental.
Within the first 10 seconds, the app should evoke curiosity or calm.
