The Focus Orb (Core Visual Identity)
The orb is always alive.
Its behavior evolves with cognitive load:
Subtle size increase as load rises
Faster pulse at higher load
Stronger glow under stress
Perfectly circular when calm
Slight organic distortion when overloaded
At high load, small particles drift away from the surface
